@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@alexToken = course-alex-local-token
@rileyToken = course-riley-local-token

### Source-derived artifact identity and configured provider posture
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/health

### Capability and data readiness are separate from artifact identity
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/readiness

### Missing credentials are a real denial, not an empty success
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/knowledge/articles

### Reset and rebuild the deterministic evidence fixture
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/reset

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/seed

###
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/demo/index

### Spoofed tenant input cannot override the authenticated principal
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/knowledge/search?q=restore%20VPN%20access%20and%20refresh%20certificate
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: tenant-red

### The other identity receives only its own tenant-visible evidence
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/knowledge/search?q=restore%20VPN%20access%20and%20enroll%20replacement%20device
Authorization: Bearer {{rileyToken}}

### Raw PII is redacted before persistence and indexing
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/support/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{alexToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Contact alex.private@example.com about SSN 123-45-6789"
}
